#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hacking &appname;"
msgstr "Hakovanje"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the spirit of Free Software, you are welcome to hack on &appname; as much "
"as you like. You should be able to write scripts to import, export, or "
"modify data very easily. This chapter gives you more information about doing "
"that."
msgstr ""
"U duhu besplatnog softvera, dobrodošli ste da hakujete &appname; koliko god "
"želite.Trebali biste biti u mogućnosti pisati skripte za uvoz, izvoz, "
"odnosno izmjenu podataka vrlo jednostavno.Ovo poglavlje daje vam više "
"informacija o tome."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Format"
msgstr "Format datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default &appname; data file is a zip archive, normally with a <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.tc</literal> file extension. Inside the archive is a top-"
"level <filename>tellico.xml</filename> file. Images may be included inside "
"the <filename>images/</filename> folder in the archive, or they may be "
"included in the &XML; data directly in a base64 encoding. Images may also be "
"saved inside the application data folder, in which case, they are not in the "
"data file at all. &appname; can also load the &XML; file, by itself, "
"uncompressed."
msgstr ""
"Zadana &appname; datoteka sa podacima je zip arhiva, normalno sa  <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.tc</literal> ekstenzijom datoteke. Unutar arhive je "
"vrhunski nivo <filename>tellico.xml</filename> datoteke. Slike mogu biti "
"unutar <filename>images/</filename> foldera u arhivi, ili mogu biti u &XML; "
"podacima izravno kodiranim u bazi 64. Slike mogu biti spašene unutar "
"foladera sa podacima aplikacije, u tom slučaju, one nisu nikako u datoteci "
"sa podacima. &appname; također može učitati &XML; datoteku nekomprimiranu, "
"samu po sebi."

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "&XML; Data"
msgstr "&XML; Podaci"

#. Tag: title
#: hacking.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collection"
msgstr "Zbirka"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: hacking.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n"
"<!DOCTYPE tellico PUBLIC \"-//Robby Stephenson/DTD Tellico V11.0//EN\" "
"\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/dtd/v11/tellico.dtd\">\n"
"<tellico xmlns=\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/\" syntaxVersion=\"11\">\n"
" <collection title=\"My Books\" type=\"2\">\n"
" </collection>\n"
"</tellico>\n"
"]]>"
msgstr ""
"<![CDATA[\n"
"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n"
"<!DOCTYPE tellico PUBLIC \"-//Robby Stephenson/DTD Tellico V11.0//EN\" "
"\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/dtd/v11/tellico.dtd\">\n"
"<tellico xmlns=\"http://periapsis.org/tellico/\" syntaxVersion=\"11\">\n"
" <collection title=\"My Books\" type=\"2\">\n"
" </collection>\n"
"</tellico>\n"
"]]>"

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file begins with the required &XML; declaration and encoding, followed "
"by the doctype. When a new field type is added or additional properties are "
"set on the default fields, the doctype DTD version is incremented. &appname; "
"is always able to open and read any previous DTD version, but will save "
"files in the current version. The DTD location does point to an actual DTD "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka počinje sa potrebnom &XML; deklaracijom i kodiranjem, zatim sa "
"tipom dokumenta. Kad se doda nova vrsta polja ili su dodatna svojstva "
"postavljena  na zadana polja, verzija tipa dokumenta DTD se povećava. "
"&appname; je uvijek u stanju da otvori i pročita bilo koju prethodnu verziju "
"DTD, ali će spasiti datoteke u trenutnoj verziji. DTD lokacija pokazuje na "
"pravu DTD datoteku."

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top-level element is a <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup> element, "
"containing the default namespace declaration and the syntax version of the "
"file, which should always match the DTD."
msgstr ""
"Element na vrhunskom nivou je <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup> element, koji "
"sadrži zadani imenski prostor  deklaracije i verziju sintakse datoteke, koja "
"treba uvijek odgovarati DTD."

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup> element contains one <markup>&lt;"
"collection&gt;</markup> element. Multiple collections are ignored, for now. "
"The <markup>title</markup> attribute contains the collection title, while "
"the <markup>type</markup> specifies what kinds of entries are contained in "
"the collection. The allowable types are in <link linkend=\"collection-type-"
"values\">listed in a later section</link>. An optional <markup>entryTitle</"
"markup> attribute may be used to specify the title of the entries for a "
"custom collection, and should be plural."
msgstr ""
"Element <markup>&lt;tellico&gt;</markup> sadrži jedan <markup>&lt;"
"collection&gt;</markup> element. Višestruke kolekcije su zanemarene, za "
"sada. <markup>title</markup> atribut sadrži naziv kolekcije, dok "
"<markup>type</markup>  određuje koje su vrste unosa sadržane u kolekciji. "
"Dozvoljeni tipovi su u <link linkend=\"collection-type-values\"> navedeni u "
"kasnijem poglavlju </link>. Opcionalni <markup>entryTitle</markup> atribut "
"može se koristiti za specifikaciju naziva unosa za prilagođenu kolekciju, i "
"treba biti u množini."

