#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&appname; will include all the default fields for a collection if the first "
"field element has the name <emphasis>_default</emphasis>. For "
"<emphasis>Paragraph</emphasis>, <emphasis>Table</emphasis>, or "
"<emphasis>Image</emphasis> fields, the field category should be identical to "
"the field title."
msgstr ""
"&appname; će uključivati sva default polja za kolekciju, ako prvi element "
"polja ima ime <emphasis>_default</emphasis>.  Za <emphasis>Paragraph</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>Table</emphasis>, ili <emphasis>Image</emphasis> polja, "
"kategorija polja bi trebala biti identična naslovu polja."

#. Tag: para
#: hacking.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The type of field is given in the type attribute of the field element. The "
"value is equal to the <type>FieldType</type> enum value in <filename>src/"
"field.h</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Tip polja je dat u tipu atributa u elementu polja. Vrijednost je jednaka "
"<type>FieldType</type> enum vrijednosti u <filename>src/field.h</filename>."

